channel.topic:
Construct a spaceship using any and all resources from Earth.
Challenge dates: July 28 – August 10 2020 at 6 PM PT

messages.content:
🚀 Spaceship Build Challenge! 🚀

Calling all explorers! Space probe MCE-R00 was launched on an adventure of the final frontier—space! The first satellite images reveal an unidentified spaceship. Unfortunately, the data was corrupted and the final appearance of the spaceship is unknown. Your build skills are needed to solve this exciting discovery!

**Your mission:** Construct a spaceship using any and all resources from Earth.

Is it from earth or extraterrestrial? Designed to carry a single lifeform or an entire crew? Grounded or in orbit? Further analysis is required… Transmission terminated. 🛰️ 

:timer: Challenge dates: July 28 – August 10, 2020 at 6 PM PT

__Challenge Guidelines__
:earth: Your creation must be built entirely by you and in Minecraft Earth.
:crafting_table: Your build must be a brand new creation, crafted just for this challenge.
:buildplate: Build your imagination! Challenge theme is open to interpretation and buildplate size won’t be a factor in judging.
:sign: Post your images or video submission and buildplate share link in #spaceship-challenge by the end date. Feel free to ask a Moderator to pin it!
:challenges_og: Submissions may be used in social media posts.
:fast_parrot: Have fun!

📡 We interrupt this programming to bring you breaking news! 🌌
The elusive **spaceship** has been identified!
The crafters of Earth determined there were not 1, but an astronomical 9 spaceships and constructed out-of-these world creations of them—including a rainbow saucer, chicken rocket, and an ominous skull-faced ship!

:challenges: The winners of the spaceship build challenge are…
:diamond: @NinjaK - Star Fighter ✈️ 
:gold: @El Brian - The First Steps 🚀
:iron: @clovepod - Taking Down the Mothership 🛸

**Congratulations to the winners and thank you to everyone who participated!** Submissions may be featured in social media posts. Checkout all the stellar builds in the 📌 pinned messages. :fast_parrot:
👀  https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/article/minecraft-earth--spaceship-challenge
